-RAT due to efficient inelastic relaxation. The\npolarization pattern observed toward IRC+10216 by SOFIA/HAWC+ can reproduced\nwhen only grains at low$-J$ attractors are present due to removal of grains at\nhigh$-J$ attractors by the RAT disruption.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Jan 2023 00:23:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-20"}
